data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! Here is your opportunity to own a piece of one of Sheboygan's beautiful historic homes in the heart of downtown Sheboygan just a few blocks from Lake Michigan! This beautiful Queen Anne home has tons of charm featuring large detailed staircases, French glass doors and massive sized rooms! A laundry room on the top floor right next to the primary bedroom! Bring your finishing ideas for the huge walk up attic space! Think; awesome play room for the kids, a cool game or entertainment room for kids/adults, etc! This well maintained property also features a large 2 car heated garage and a quaint patio outback for chilling or entertaining. Walk to your favorite dining and shopping locations as well as Sheboygan's cool downtown events or the beach! You have to see this in person
